# Egress policy — working rules

Governed by `@standards/networking/egress-policy/SKILL.md`. Enforced by
`@standards/networking/egress-policy/conformance/test_conformance.py`.

- **EGR-001** Explicit destination per dependency — no `*` hosts.
- **EGR-002** Default deny — no `0.0.0.0/0` unless SME-ratified in the PR.

Emit `integration.params.json` first; render NetworkPolicy or Nomad egress from it.
